## Information Collection and Use

We collect data that you provide to us through the use of our service.

This
includes the keywords entered into the expertQuery parameter.

## Log Data

When you use our service, our servers automatically record information ("log
data"), including information that your browser sends whenever you visit a
website.

This log data may include your IP address, browser type, the pages of
our service that you visit, and other statistics.
